== 藝術展覽 ==

劉玉玲曾以「玉玲」展示她的作品。<ref name="NYTimes">{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2009/03/07/arts/design/07armo.html |title=Toplessness and Taxidermy in a Bottoming Market |newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |first=Karen |last=Rosenberg |date=March 6, 2009 |accessdate=December 6, 2019 |archive-date=2020-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129191708/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/03/07/arts/design/07armo.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>劉玉玲擅長多種藝術媒介，曾舉辦過畫廊展覽展示她的[[拼貼畫|拼貼畫]]，繪畫和攝影作品。<ref name="Liu2">{{cite magazine| last =Tucker| first =Reed| title =Painting By Numbers With Lucy Liu| magazine =Esquire| date =May 1, 2006| url =https://www.esquire.com/entertainment/a1303/esq0506lucyliu-124/| accessdate =December 6, 2019| archive-date =2020-08-03| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20200803124031/https://www.esquire.com/entertainment/a1303/esq0506lucyliu-124/| dead-url =no}}</ref>她從16歲起就開始做混合媒介拼貼，後來成為攝影師和畫家。<ref name="regis">[[Live_with_Regis_and_Kelly|Live with Regis and Kelly]]. First aired on January 21, 2008.</ref>劉玉玲在2004年至2006年期間就讀於紐約工作室學校，學習有關繪畫，繪畫和雕塑的課程。<ref name="auto">{{cite web |url=http://www.gg-art.com/news/read.php?newsid=6434 |title=''Acting out her art – CAN life be any more unfair?'', January 24, 2008. |publisher=www.gg-art.com |accessdate=May 21, 2013 |archive-date=2020-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803172439/http://www.gg-art.com/news/read.php?newsid=6434 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2006年9月，劉玉玲舉行了一場藝術展，並將其所得的利潤捐贈給了[[聯合國兒童基金會|聯合國兒童基金會]]。<ref name="regis" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mcmurry.com/about/about_news_release.asp?contentid=4741 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061126173246/http://www.mcmurry.com/about/about_news_release.asp?contentid=4741 |archive-date=2006-11-26 |title=''Auction of Lucy Liu's Artwork Raises More Than $330,000'', October 17, 2006. |publisher=Mcmurry.com |accessdate=March 8, 2010 |df= |dead-url=no }}</ref>她還於2008年在慕尼黑舉行了另一場展覽。她的畫作《逃逸》被併入[[萬寶龍|萬寶龍]]的《尖端藝術》收藏中，並在2008年邁阿密巴塞爾藝術展上展出，該展覽展示了當代美國藝術家的作品。劉玉玲表示，她將自己從紐約市牛奶畫廊展覽中獲得的利潤捐贈給了[[聯合國兒童基金會|聯合國兒童基金會]]。<ref>{{cite web |title=Custom Content Council |url=http://www.customcontentcouncil.com/news/auction-lucy-lius-artwork-raises-more-330000 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413124000/http://www.customcontentcouncil.com/news/auction-lucy-lius-artwork-raises-more-330000 |archivedate=2014-04-13 |accessdate=2019-12-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>在倫敦，她的畫作《七十二》中的一部分收入捐給了了[[聯合國兒童基金會|聯合國兒童基金會]]。<ref name="UNICEF">{{cite web |title=UNICEF |url=http://www.unicefusa.org/partners/ambassadors/lucy-liu.html |accessdate=2019-12-24 |archive-date=2014-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413140357/http://www.unicefusa.org/partners/ambassadors/lucy-liu.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

她的第一次國家博物館展覽於2019年初在新加坡國家博物館舉行。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.silverkris.com/interview-lucy-liu-art-acting-identity/|title=Interview: Lucy Liu on art, acting and identity|date=2019-02-08|website=SilverKris|language=en-GB|access-date=2019-02-19|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030195630/https://www.silverkris.com/interview-lucy-liu-art-acting-identity/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

